e%20technology%20to%20the%20war%20effort%20became%20increasingly%20clearer%2C%20Ukraine%20sought%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20officials%20saying%20the%20country%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-will-produce-over-1-million-drones-this-year-official-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduce%20more%20than%20a%20million%20drones%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20also%20said%20it%20would%20be%20boosting%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%202030%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20produce%2032%2C000%20drones%20%5Bannually%5D%2C%20covering%20around%2070%25%20%5Bof%20Russia's%20needs%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20defense%20minister%20Andrei%20Belousov%20said%20last%20year%2C%20per%20Russia's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftass.com%2Feconomy%2F1610899%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETass%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20experts%20told%20Defense%20One%20the%20US%20was%20likely%20producing%20far%20fewer%20drones%20than%20this%2C%20possibly%20up%20to%20just%20a%20few%20thousand%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20drone%20warfare%2C%20the%20side%20with%20the%20most%20powerful%20tech%20does%20not%20necessarily%20hold%20the%20advantage%2C%20rather%20it%20is%20the%20side%20with%20the%20largest%20stocks%20and%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20quickly%20mass%20produce%20and%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20could%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20long%20relied%20instead%20on%20building%20large%2C%20advanced%20systems%20like%20the%20MQ-9%20Reaper%20drone%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20at%20around%20%2430%20million%20each%2C%20have%20nevertheless%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthis-downed-3rd-us-reaper-drone-worth-30m-1-month-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etough%20year%20battling%20the%20Houthi%20rebels%20around%20Yemen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20number%20going%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20small%20FPV%20drone%20is%20not%20such%20a%20big%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20drone%20manufacturers%20such%20as%20Skydio%20could%20boost%20their%20production%20levels%20to%20help%20level%20the%20playing%20field%2C%20but%20they%20face%20stiff%20global%20sales%20competition%20from%20Chinese%20firms%2C%20which%20have%20large%20research%20teams%20and%20can%20often%20offer%20far%20cheaper%20drones%20to%20prospective%20buyers%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20global%20drone%20industry%2C%20but%20US%20authorities%20consider%20firms%20like%20China's%20DJI%20a%20security%20threat%20and%20have%20proposed%20to%20effectively%20ban%20new%20sales%20of%20them%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20they%20are%20still%20the%20go-to%20option%20for%20many%20US%20operators%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnational-security%2Fcongresss-plan-to-outlaw-chinese-drones-met-with-protest-c95cf1fe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20emergency%20services%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20Gury%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Performance%20Drone%20Works%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20companies%20like%20DJI%20%26quot%3Bhad%20a%20huge%20head%20start.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gury%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthose%20drones%20are%20made%20for%20consumers%2C%20amateurs%2C%20hobbyists%2C%20or%20cinematography.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20future%20of%20warfare%20will%20be%20surrounded%20by%20small%20robotics%2C%20small%20sensors%20that%20can%20be%20deployed%20by%20small%20fire%20teams%2C%20units%2C%20and%20single%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Gury%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20defense%20and%20our%20ability%20to%20innovate%20are%20still%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20leading%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20the%20US%20must%20now%20find%20a%20way%20to%20stimulate%20demand%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20boost%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20the%20U.S.%20military%20mainstreams%20operational%20concepts%20that%20demand%20large%20numbers%20of%20drones%2C%20production%20will%20remain%20at%20a%20relatively%20low%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Bryan%20Clark%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20and%20director%20at%20the%20Hudson%20Institute's%20Center%20for%20Defense%20Concepts%20and%20Technology%2C%20told%20Defense%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Benowitz%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20drone%20market%20firm%20DroneAnalyst%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20the%20military%20would%20also%20have%20to%20increase%20drone%20orders%20if%20it%20has%20ambitions%20of%20closing%20the%20price%20and%20capacity%20gaps%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gury%20noted%20that%20not%20just%20any%20drones%20will%20do%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20use%20GPS%20anymore%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20It's%20easily%20jammed.%20You%20need%20systems%20that%20use%20satellite%20imagery%20to%20look%20at%20the%20ground.%20You%20need%20radio%20systems%20designed%20to%20overcome%20electronic%20warfare.%20You%20need%20drones%20that%20perform%20well%20at%20night%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20tactical%20environments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drone-production-may-not-be-sufficient-potential-wartime-report-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723453823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b63196b4912df3ae1a46a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drone-production-may-not-be-sufficient-potential-wartime-report-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20say%20the%20US%20must%20find%20a%20way%20to%20stimulate%20demand%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20boost%20drone%20production%20and%20close%20the%20gap%20with%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider