Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESusie%20Moore%20is%20a%20former%20sales%20director%20and%20current%20life%20coach.%3Cp%3ESusie%20Moore%20Int.%20LLC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EManaging%20emotions%20is%20crucial%20for%20business%20success%2C%20says%20entrepreneur%20Susie%20Moore.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMoore%20became%20a%207-figure%20business%20owner%20by%20learning%20to%20accept%20rejection%20and%20deal%20with%20internet%20hate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20advises%20business%20owners%20to%20be%20cautious%20of%20lifestyle%20creep%20and%20understand%20your%20team%20isn't%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20is%20simply%20a%20blend%20of%20math%20and%20emotions.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-warren-buffett-spends-money-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUntil%20you%20can%20manage%20your%20emotions%2C%20don't%20expect%20to%20manage%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20part%20is%20easy%20to%20understand.%20Emotions%20are%20the%20messy%20part.%20We%20attach%20meaning%20and%20self-worth%20to%20money%2C%20which%20halts%20our%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20career%20in%20sales%20and%20business%20development%20in%20adtech%20in%202007%20and%20became%20a%20full-time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsusie-moore.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014.%20Conversations%20I've%20had%20about%20divorce%2C%20politics%2C%20parenting%2C%20and%20sexuality%20were%20less%20emotionally%20charged%20than%20conversations%20around%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20high%20school%20education%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildren-of-parents-on-welfare-are-more-likely-to-be-on-welfare-2013-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrew%20up%20on%20welfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20now%20an%20entrepreneur%20with%20a%207-figure%20business%2C%20I%20know%20that%20managing%20my%20emotions%20is%20my%20most%20underrated%20success%20tool.%20Here's%20how%20I%20manage%20six%20of%20the%20most%20common%20business%20frustrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248edd4c2-9126-4025-a2cd-1476c38d8f45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20sting%20of%20rejection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20weep%20at%20the%20opportunities%20people%20around%20me%20have%20lost%20because%20they%20fear%20hearing%20%26quot%3Bno.%26quot%3B%20Every%20human%20success%20story%20is%20littered%20with%20rejections%20and%20disappointments%20(this%20is%20why%20I'm%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Finspiring-autobiographies-everyone-should-read-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereading%20autobiographies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20say%20the%20same%20thing).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20most%20people%2C%20upon%20getting%20rejected%2C%20stop%20or%20gently%20try%20something%20once%20again%2C%20I%20keep%20going.%20As%20a%20former%20sales%20director%20for%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%2C%20I%20know%20that%20success%20usually%20comes%20down%20to%20volume.%20The%20more%20exposure%2C%20the%20more%20meetings%2C%20and%20the%20more%20visibility%2C%20the%20more%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20bounce-back%20rate%20after%20a%20rejection%20has%20gone%20from%20one%20to%20two%20days%20to%20one%20to%20two%20minutes.%20I%20wish%20it%20were%20as%20simple%20as%20taking%20a%20deep%20breath%20or%20repeating%20a%20mantra%2C%20but%20it's%20pure%20acceptance%20around%20the%20inevitability%20of%20rejection.%20Not%20everyone%20is%20the%20perfect%20fit%2C%20or%20the%20timing%20isn't%20right.%20It's%20just%20not%20that%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f1c3368-29ec-4e52-8868-80154e5c9d13%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Refunds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERefunds%20aren't%20a%20personal%20attack%2C%20but%20refund%20requests%20used%20to%20drive%20me%20into%20a%20sensitivity%20frenzy%20when%20I%20started%20my%20business.%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20up%20at%20a%20customer's%20house%20and%20plead%20my%20case.%20%3Cem%3EWhat's%20wrong%3F%20Don't%20you%20see%20the%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Evalue%20here%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20view%20refunds%20as%20a%20standard%20line%20item%20on%20the%20P%26amp%3BL%20%E2%80%94%20with%20indifference%20as%20long%20as%20they%20stay%20below%20a%203-5%25%20threshold.%20I%20actually%20congratulate%20new%20business%20owners%20on%20refund%20requests.%20In%20any%20industry%2C%20there's%20no%20scaling%20a%20business%20without%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b371d308-8181-4428-864a-33e83d7759f3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Internet%20trolls%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20refunds%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternet-trolls-get-a-kick-out-of-making-others-upset-for-this-reason-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrolls%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20part%20of%20every%20business%20owner's%20story.%20My%20hairdresser%20told%20me%20about%20a%20Yelp%20review%20that%20made%20her%20cry.%20I%20told%20her%20to%20snap%20out%20of%20it%20and%20get%20used%20to%20it%20if%20she%20wants%20to%20have%20a%20future%20working%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20avoiding%20negative%2C%20non-constructive%20feedback.%20I've%20had%20comments%20that%20vary%20from%20sexist%20remarks%20(%26quot%3BWho%20is%20she%20sleeping%20with%20to%20earn%20that%20much%3F%26quot%3B)%20to%20statements%20about%20my%20looks%20(%26quot%3BYou%20look%20like%20a%20man%20%E2%80%94%20you%20need%20to%20do%20something%20about%20that%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20heart%20used%20to%20sink%20when%20I%20read%20a%20mean%20remark%2C%20and%20I'd%20even%20look%20the%20person%20up%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20them.%20Now%2C%20I%20rarely%20even%20see%20them%2C%20and%20I%20certainly%20don't%20go%20looking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20criticism%20hurts%2C%20but%20when%20you%20realize%20that%20the%20worst%20a%20mean%20comment%20can%20do%20is%20make%20you%20sad%20or%20scared%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20it%20loses%20all%20power%20over%20you.%20It%20becomes%20something%20you%20expect%20rather%20than%20fear.%20If%20you're%20sincere%20and%20ambitious%2C%20expect%20it%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22884e1dcf-9478-475c-b3dc-85b203f67712%5C%22%3E4.%20S%3Cstrong%3Elow%20or%20non-growth%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20thing%20any%20entrepreneur%20can%20do%20is%20make%20fear-based%20decisions.%20If%20you've%20allowed%20spending%20creep%20%E2%80%94%20most%20commonly%20overstaffing%20and%2For%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Flifestyle-creep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20income%20increases%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20likely%20to%20make%20poor%2C%20hasty%20decisions%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20downturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreadwinner-wife-husband-quit-job-relationship-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20his%20finance%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20work%20full-time%20with%20me%20in%202017.%20When%20scaling%20our%20products%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20video%20production%20team%2C%20an%20SEO%20consultant%2C%20and%20an%20admin%20assistant.%20Since%20then%2C%20we've%20scaled%20back%20and%20now%20only%20work%20with%20one%20full-time%20operations%20director%20and%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20live%20in%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment.%20These%20are%20conscious%20choices%20that%20we're%20thrilled%20with.%20Impressing%20other%20people%20is%20not%20my%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20year%20is%20%26quot%3Bup%20and%20to%20the%20right!%26quot%3B%20because%20business%20has%20seasons.%20Whenever%20we%20hit%20a%20plateau%2C%20I%20know%20I%20need%20to%20test%20new%20marketing%20strategies%2C%20increase%20visibility%2C%20and%2For%20add%20to%20my%20product%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20slower%20season%20can%20feel%20worrisome%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20an%20invitation%20to%20reflect%20and%20ask%20focused%20questions%2C%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20working%2C%20and%20how%20can%20we%20do%20more%20of%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20I%20get%20people%20even%20better%20results%20so%20that%20my%20work%20sells%20itself%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b53207ec-4c16-4c79-b633-6fee7d01a793%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Staff%20moving%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETeams%20sometimes%20feel%20like%20family%2C%20but%20they're%20not.%20All%20business%20is%20simply%20an%20exchange%20of%20value%20between%20parties%2C%20which%20also%20applies%20to%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20and%20industry%20you%20work%20in%20at%2030%20isn't%20necessarily%20the%20right%20job%20or%20industry%20for%20you%20at%2035.%20It's%20appropriate%20and%20healthy%20for%20people%20to%20move%20on%20when%20the%20time%20is%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20successful%20businesses%20are%20constantly%20evolving.%20I%20have%20what%20feels%20like%20a%20new%20company%20every%20six%20months.%20Some%20people%20won't%20go%20in%20new%20creative%20directions%20with%20you%2C%20and%20that's%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287353872-0b54-413f-823a-66b4f3c00cbb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Being%20%26quot%3Boverlooked%26quot%3B%20for%20opportunities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20once%20fully%20prepared%20for%20a%20national%20morning%20show%20TV%20appearance.%20The%20day%20before%2C%20the%20producer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20turning%20this%20into%20a%20group%20'Momversation'%20with%20Mother's%20Day%20coming%20up.%20Do%20you%20have%20kids%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%2C%20and%20I%20lost%20my%20spot.%20I%20was%20so%20disappointed%20that%20I%20went%20for%20a%20long%20walk%2C%20called%20three%20close%20pals%20to%20complain%2C%20and%20sank%20three%20glasses%20of%20wine.%20I%20allowed%20myself%20the