20the%20Netherlands%20beat%20refugee%20team%20member%20B-Girl%20Talash%20in%20the%20first%20ever%20breaking%20battle%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%93%B8%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FParis2024%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Paris2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FmPRuFTOVMN%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FmPRuFTOVMN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20The%20Khel%20India%202.0%20(%40BharatAtOlympic)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBharatAtOlympic%2Fstatus%2F1821940121098166342%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20b-girls%20and%20b-boys%2C%20India%20Sardjoe%20prefers%20using%20her%20real%20name%20as%20her%20stage%20name.%20She%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first-ever%20winner%20of%20a%20breaking%20battle%20at%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20India%20started%20playing%20football%20as%20a%20child%20before%20switching%20to%20hip-hop%20and%20later%20transitioned%20to%20breakdancing.%20At%20just%2010%20years%20old%2C%20she%20won%20the%20Dutch%20national%20championship%20in%20the%20Under%2012%20category.%20She%20then%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20Dutch%2C%20European%20and%20world%20champion%20in%20the%20span%20of%20just%20six%20months%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20confusion%20surrounding%20India's%20participation%20in%20breaking%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20has%20been%20put%20to%20rest%2C%20with%20the%20country%20actually%20fielding%20117%20athletes%20across%20various%20sports%20and%20bringing%20home%20six%20medals%20-%20five%20bronze%20and%20one%20silver.%20The%20participating%20countries%20in%20breaking%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20were%20Canada%2C%20Japan%2C%20France%2C%20Lithuania%2C%20China%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Breaking%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20is%20a%20high-energy%20dance%20style%20that%20started%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%201970s.%20It%20grew%20out%20of%20hip-hop%20culture%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20New%20York%2C%20where%20block%20parties%20were%20all%20the%20rage.%20Breaking%20is%20known%20for%20its%20acrobatic%20moves%2C%20slick%20footwork%20and%20the%20important%20role%20of%20the%20DJ%20and%20MC%20in%20hyping%20up%20the%20crowd%20during%20battles.%20By%20the%201990s%2C%20breaking%20had%20spread%20globally%2C%20with%20international%20competitions%20that%20helped%20it%20gain%20popularity%20among%20hip-hop%20fans%20and%20beyond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20made%20its%20Olympic%20debut%20in%20Paris.%20The%20dance%20form%20was%20first%20introduced%20at%20the%202018%20Summer%20Youth%20Olympic%20Games%20in%20Buenos%20Aires.%20Due%20to%20its%20success%2C%20it%20was%20added%20to%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympic%20program%20as%20a%20new%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fb-girl-india-paris-2024-athletes-watch-series-profile%5C%22%3EOlympics%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%2C%20Ms%20India%20said%20that%20she%20had%20already%20made%20history%20considering%20%26quot%3Bit's%20the%20first%20time%20Breaking%20is%20at%20the%20Olympics.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20such%20a%20highlight%20in%20the%20Breaking%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723450380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fg9b1hclk_india-sardjoe-getty_625x300_12_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findia-makes-history-at-breaking-in-paris-olympics-2024-but-is-it-really-india-6318404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20quest%20for%20gold%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20has%20come%20to%20an%20end%20after%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20silver%20in%20the%20javelin%20throw%20final.%20But%2C%20in%20a%20surprising%20twist%2C%20'India'%20has%20made%20history%20in%20the%20sport%20of%20Br