le%20phone%20was%20full%20of%20pornographic%20material%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoy%20was%20arrested%20after%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20on%20the%20hospital%20premises%20captured%20him%20entering%20the%20emergency%20building%20around%204%20am%20on%20Friday%3B%20the%20doctor's%20body%20was%20found%20in%20the%20same%20building%20hours%20later.%20Another%20big%20clue%20was%20a%20Bluetooth%20headset%20found%20next%20to%20the%20victim's%20body.%20The%20CCTV%20footage%20showed%20the%20headset%20round%20Roy's%20neck%20when%20he%20enters%20the%20building.%20It%20was%20missing%20when%20he%20exited.%20The%20headset%20next%20to%20the%20victim's%20body%20also%20paired%20with%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Roy%20went%20home%20after%20committing%20the%20heinous%20crime%20and%20washed%20his%20clothes%20to%20destroy%20evidence.%20Police%20have%2C%20however%2C%20found%20bloodstains%20on%20his%20shoes.%20The%20accused%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20police%20custody%20till%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor's%20horrifying%20rape%20and%20murder%20on%20duty%20have%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests.%20Amid%20the%20agitation%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20medical%20college%20has%20resigned.%20Questions%20have%20been%20raised%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20if%20everyone%20enjoyed%20unabated%20access%20to%20the%20premises%20at%20odd%20hours%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20on%20this%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprincipal-of-kolkata-medical-college-where-trainee-doctor-was-raped-and-murdered-resigns-amid-student-protests-6318489%5C%22%3EPrincipal%20Quits%20After%20Kolkata%20Doctor%20Rape-Murder%2C%20Protests%20Across%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723449120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2fiichd_kolkata-doctor-rape-accused_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rap