do-system-scaling-tests-musk-reveals-plan-ahead-of-his-interview-with-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F112456364.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fam-going-to-do-system-scaling-tests-musk-reveals-plan-ahead-of-his-interview-with-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F112456364.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20We%20Had%20Not%20Helped%20Her...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20On%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPraising%20the%20Centre%20for%20giving%20refuge%20to%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20after%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20as%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20amid%20violent%20protests%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20power%20shift%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20for%20worry%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20views%20on%20how%20the%20developments%20in%20Bangladesh%20would%20impact%20its%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20fundamental%20interest%20lies%20in%20close%20and%20friendly%20relations%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%20our%20basic%20commitment%20is%20to%20the%20well-being%20of%20Bangladesh%20people%2C%20the%20State%20comes%20second%20and%20any%20individual%20leader%20comes%20third.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20we%20were%20with%20them%20in%201971%2C%20we%20have%20been%20with%20them%20through%20thick%20and%20thin%2C%20even%20when%20they%20had%20governments%20who%20were%20less%20than%20friendly%20to%20us%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20keep%20our%20relationship%20on%20an%20even%20keel%20and%20certainly%20there%20should%20be%20no%20deterioration%20in%20that%20relationship%20in%20time%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fnn1b5018_shashi-tharoor_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20interim%20government%20headed%20by%20Nobel%20peace%20prize%20winner%20and%20Grameen%20Bank%20founder%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20no%20cause%20for%20anxiety%20for%20New%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20personally%2C%20he%20is%20a%20highly%20respected%20figure.%20I%20suppose%20he%20is%20somewhat%20close%20to%20Washington%20rather%20than%20being%20seen%20as%20close%20to%20Jamaat%20e%20Islami%20or%20Pakistani%20ISI.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20composition%20of%20the%20interim%20government%2C%20there%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20particular%20reason%20for%20India%20to%20feel%20any%20anxiety%20about%20countries%20hostile%20to%20us%20having%20put%20their%20stamp%20on%20this%20interim%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20concern%20for%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20always%20been%20whether%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20will%20fish%20in%20troubled%20waters.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20kind%20of%20context%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20possibility%20that%20the%20Pakistani%20ISI%20could%20have%20had%20a%20hand%20in%20some%20outrageous%20incidents%20of%20violence%20during%20the%20agitation%2C%20that%20the%20Chinese%20who%20have%20a%20strong%20presence%20in%20Bangladesh%20might%20have%20seen%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20expand%20their%20influence%2C%20those%20are%20things%20people%20watching%20relations%20in%20the%20subcontinent%20are%20most%20concerned%20about.%20But%20certainly%20there%20is%20no%20implication%20of%20anything%20in%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20interim%20government%20or%20the%20initial%20statements%20of%20Mr%20Yunus%20that%20would%20give%20us%20any%20cause%20for%20worry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20underlining%20the%20interim%20leader's%20call%20for%20peace%20and%20protection%20of%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India%20giving%20refuge%20to%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20following%20her%20ouster%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20had%20words%20of%20praise%20for%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20not%20helped%20her%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20disgrace%20for%20India.%20Nobody%20would%20have%20wanted%20to%20be%20our%20friend%20if%20we%20had%20treated%20our%20friend%20badly.%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20India%20and%20India%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20her.%20And%20when%20a%20friend%20is%20in%20trouble%2C%20you%20don't%20look%20twice%20before%20you%20help%20them%2C%20keep%20them%20safe.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20India%20has%20done.%20I%20applaud%20the%20government%20for%20doing%20it.%20I%20would%20have%20wanted%20nothing%20less.%20As%20an%20Indian%2C%20we%20have%20certain%20standards%20we%20stand%20for%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20government%20has%20done%20right%20thing%20to%20bring%20her%20here%20and%20ensure%20her%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20long%20she%20wishes%20to%20remain%20is%20not%20for%20us.%20You%20don't%20call%20someone%20to%20your%20house%20and%20ask%20them%20when%20are%20you%20leaving.%20My%20view%20is%20we%20wait%20and%20see%2C%20how%20long%20she%20feels%20she%20can%20stay%20before%20she%20moves%20on.%20There%20are%20practical%20considerations%20before%20moving%20to%20any%20other%20country%2C%20there%20ae%20visa%20considerations%2C%20other%20issues.%20For%20now%2C%20She%20is%20with%20us%20and%20we%20should%20be%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20stood%20by%20a%20friend%20when%20her%20personal%20safety%20was%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20response%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20Indian%20government%20should%20raise%20concerns%20regarding%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20more%20forcefully%2C%20he%20conflicting%20reports%20are%20coming%20out%20of%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BThere%20