tion%20and%20natural%20remedies%2C%20like%20coca%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Fjournals%2Fpsychiatry%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyt.2023.1221047%2Ffull%23h6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrontiers%20in%20Psychiatry%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20while%3Cspan%3E%20episodes%20of%20psychosis%20during%20exposure%20to%20high%20altitude%20are%20frequently%20reported%2C%20it%20has%20still%20not%20been%20assigned%20to%20medical%20diagnoses.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22748657bd-a3d0-4477-82a4-fafc0aec3c3f%5C%22%3EStaying%20safe%20at%20altitude%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20have%20been%20in%20serious%20trouble%20if%20not%20for%20my%20guide.%20He%20rapidly%20identified%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20carried%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-wish-i-packed-on-first-long-distance-hike-mistakes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eday%20pack%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way%2C%20and%20helped%20me%20ascend%20slowly%20to%20high%20camp.%20Once%20there%2C%20he%20gave%20me%20spoonfuls%20of%20raw%20sugar%20and%20plenty%20of%20water%20and%20descended%20with%20me%20at%20first%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20love%20multi-day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiking-patagonia-argentina-trekking-poles-would-have-helped-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrekking%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mountain%20climbing.%20I%20just%20recently%20got%20back%20from%20a%20four-day%20journey%20through%20the%20high%20Caucasus%2C%20where%20I%20had%20to%20scurry%20up%20steep%20rock%20scrambles%2C%20ford%20glacially%20fed%20rivers%2C%20and%20walk%20heel-to-toe%20down%20weaving%2C%20sharply%20declining%20cow%20paths%20for%2015%20miles%20per%20day.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mountains%20are%20majestic%20and%20restorative%2C%20but%20they%20must%20be%20respected%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20have%20new%20rules%20for%20staying%20both%20mentally%20and%20physically%20safe%20at%20altitude%20and%20on%20extreme%20outdoor%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20hiking%20in%20the%20High%20Caucasus%20in%20Svaneti%2C%20Georgia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b97a70955b01c3294d8fcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20been%20hiking%20recently%20in%20the%20High%20Caucasus%20in%20Svaneti%2C%20Georgia.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%20Lavis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-pack-everest-base-camp-trek-packing-tips-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProper%20acclimatization%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20first%20rule.%20I%20like%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20days%20adjusting%20to%20my%20new%20altitude.%20I%20lay%20low%20the%20first%20day%20or%20two%20and%20take%20a%20tentative%2C%20exploratory%2C%20short%20hike%20on%20the%20third%20or%20fourth.%20Doing%20this%20allows%20me%20to%20assess%20how%20my%20body%20is%20performing%20and%20regulating%20at%20the%20new%20heights%2C%20and%20a%20shorter%2C%20less%20intense%20hike%20lets%20me%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20on%20a%20longer%20slog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20limit%20the%20amount%20of%20over-the-counter%20medicine%20I%20take%2C%20powering%20through%20the%20first%20few%20fuzzy%20days%20of%20headache%20and%20fatigue%20until%20my%20body%20resettles%20itself.%20I%20still%20drink%20coca%20tea%20to%20ward%20off%20some%20symptoms%2C%20but%20by%20listening%20to%20my%20body%2C%20I%20can%20ensure%20that%20it's%20functioning%20optimally%20and%20ready%20for%20the%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I've%20learned%20to%20be%20more%20humble.%20While%20I%20was%20fairly%20fit%20and%20prepared%20to%20climb%20Huayna%20Potosi%2C%20I%20didn't%20consider%20the%20mental%20or%20extreme%20physical%20toll%20the%20mountain%20would%20take.%20Knowing%20your%20l