2Iconic%20Statue%20Of%20Pakistan%20Army's%201971%20Surrender%20Vandalised%20In%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20statue%20meant%20to%20commemorate%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh%20has%20been%20destroyed%20by%20%26quot%3Banti-India%20vandals%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20said%20today.%20Mr%20Tharoor%20shared%20an%20image%20of%20the%20broken%20statue%20which%20depicted%20the%20moment%20Pakistan%20surrendered%20after%20the%201971%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSad%20to%20see%20images%20like%20this%20of%20statues%20at%20the%201971%20Shaheed%20Memorial%20Complex%2C%20Mujibnagar%2C%20destroyed%20by%20anti-India%20vandals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20follows%20disgraceful%20attacks%20on%20the%20Indian%20cultural%20centre%2C%20temples%2C%20and%20Hindu%20homes%20in%20several%20places%2C%20even%20as%20reports%20came%20in%20of%20Muslim%20civilians%20protecting%20other%20minority%20homes%20and%20places%20of%20worship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESad%20to%20see%20images%20like%20this%20of%20statues%20at%20the%201971%20Shaheed%20Memorial%20Complex%2C%20Mujibnagar%2C%20destroyed%20by%20anti-India%20vandals.%20This%20follows%20disgraceful%20attacks%20on%20the%20Indian%20cultural%20centre%2C%20temples%20and%20Hindu%20homes%20in%20several%20places%2C%20even%20as%20reports%20came%20in%20of%20Muslim%20civilians%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFFrftoA81T%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFFrftoA81T%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20(%40ShashiTharoor)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShashiTharoor%2Fstatus%2F1822830968702750934%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201971%20war%20not%20only%20liberated%20Bangladesh%20but%20also%20dealt%20Pakistan%20a%20crushing%20blow.%20The%20statue%20depicted%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20'Instrument%20Of%20Surrender'%20by%20Pakistan%20Army%20Major-General%20Amir%20Abdullah%20Khan%20Niazi%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Bangladesh's%20Mukti%20Bahini.%20Major-General%20Niazi%20surrendered%20with%20his%2093%2C000%20troops%20before%20Lt%20General%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Aurora%2C%20then%20General%20Officer%20Commanding-in-Chief%20of%20India's%20Eastern%20Command.%20This%20was%20the%20largest%20military%20surrender%20since%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student-led%20uprising%20in%20Bangladesh%20has%20led%20to%20the%20resignation%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20and%20several%20other%20top%20officials.%20At%20least%20450%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20more%20than%20a%20month%20of%20deadly%20protests%20that%20led%20to%20Hasina's%20exit%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHasina%20faces%20allegations%20of%20murder%2C%20forced%20disappearance%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20and%20corruption%2C%20and%20must%20face%20the%20law%2C%20Amir%20Khosru%20Mahmud%20Chowdhury%2C%20a%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20have%20also%20been%20severely%20harsh%20on%20Hindus%20residing%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20several%20attacks%20against%20Hindu%20households%2C%20temples%2C%20and%20businesses.%20Hindus%20are%20the%20largest%20minority%20faith%20in%20mostly%20Muslim%20Bangladesh%20and%20are%20considered%20a%20steadfast%20support%20base%20for%20Hasina's%20party%2C%20the%20Awami%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20minority%20communities%20in%20the%20violence-hit%20nation%20have%20faced%20more%20than%20205%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20across%2052%20districts%20since%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20Tharoor%20urged%20the%20new%20caretaker%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammed%20Yunus%2C%20to%20take%20urgent%20steps%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agenda%20of%20some%20of%20the%20agitators%20is%20quite%20clear.%20It%20is%20essential%20that%20Muhammed%20Yunus%20and%20his%20interim%20government%20take%20urgent%20steps%20to%20restore%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20all%20Bangladeshis%2C%20of%20every%20faith.%20India%20stands%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh%20at%20this%20turbulent%20time%2C%20but%20such%20anarchic%20excess%20can%20never%20be%20condoned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723436820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fbvrfkol_bangladesh-war-memorial-vandalised_625x300_12_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-protest-anti-hindu-attacks-iconic-statue-of-pakistan-army-1971-surrender-vandalised-in-bangladesh-6318144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20statue%20meant%20to%20commemorate%20the%20liberation%20of%20Bangladesh%20has%20been%20destroyed%20by%20%26quot%3Banti-India%20vandals%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-protest-anti-hindu-attacks-iconic-statue-of-pakistan-army-1971-surrender-vandalised-in-bangladesh-6318144%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20firefighters%20tackle%20wildfire%20as%20smoke%20fills%20skyline%20above%20Greek%20capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723436640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-greece-athens-wildfires_6654352.jpg%3F20240812051922%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhundreds-of-firefighters-tackle-wildfire-near-greek-capital-athens-13195819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20wildfire%20is%20burning%20jus