ted%20lakes%20helps%20recharge%20groundwater%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20steps%20involved%20in%20the%20lake%20rejuvenation%20drives%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20first%2C%20they%20identify%20the%20lakes%20that%20need%20urgent%20rejuvenation.%20Secondly%2C%20they%20prepare%20a%20detailed%20project%20report%20(DPR)%2C%20which%20includes%20information%20on%20the%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20topography%2C%20ecology%2C%20funds%2C%20and%20everything%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20benefit%20the%20community%20and%20biodiversity.%20Thirdly%2C%20they%20obtain%20approval%20from%20the%20government%20authorities.%20Finally%2C%20they%20proceed%20with%20the%20restoration%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kapil%2C%20rejuvenating%20polluted%20lakes%20helps%20with%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20builds%20resilience%20against%20urban%20flooding%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20lake%20can%20store%20up%20to%20200%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20every%20monsoon.%20Imagine%20gallons%20of%20rainwater%20flowing%20down%20the%20drain%20and%20flooding%20the%20city.%20Lakes%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20capture%20that%20rainwater%2C%20which%20can%20then%20support%20the%20city%20during%20the%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKapil%20aims%20to%20restore%2015%20more%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20before%20the%20next%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20miles%20away%20from%20India%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20in%20the%20US%20since%202015%2C%20but%20this%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20affected%20the%20organisation%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20only%20grown%20since%20then.%20Although%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20visit%20home%20often%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20my%20parents%20angry!%20%E2%80%94%20I%20ensure%20to%20return%20to%20India%20once%20every%20year%20to%20monitor%20the%