hs%20we%20could%20take%20to%20reach%20our%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Geet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20participated%20in%20debates%2C%20team%20building%20activities%2C%20made%20rockets%2C%20leadership%20activities%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20reinforced%20my%20passion%20for%20space%20exploration.%20I%20have%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20my%20academic%20and%20career%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Class%2011%20student%20at%2021K%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20won%20the%20Right%20Stuff%20award%2C%20given%20to%20an%20outstanding%20camper%20who%20excels%20not%20only%20in%20skills%20and%20tasks%20but%20also%20embodies%20an%20exceptional%20attitude%2C%20team%20spirit%2C%20and%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20aims%20to%20pursue%20a%20Bachelors%20degree%20in%20astrophysics%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20or%C2%A0Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%20(IISER)%20or%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20could%20also%20enrol%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketcenter.com%2FSpaceCamp%2FAdvancedAcademy%23block-usrcapiblock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Geet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723210097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgeett-1723203096.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360476%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Geet%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%2011%20from%20Delhi%20participated%20in%20the%20NASA%20Space%20Camp%20at%20the%20US%20Space%20and%20Rocket%20Center%20in%20June%202024.%20Geet%20was%20just%20five%20when%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20space.%20What%20followed%20soon%20was%20her%20ambition%20to%20become%20an%20astrophysicist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360476%2Fnasa-space-camp-for-students-astronauts-geet-alabama-us-space-rocket-centre-how-to-get-apply%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20Uses%20Corn%20Waste%20to%20Make%20Bags%20That%20Decompose%20in%20180%20Days%3B%20Replaced%206%20Million%20Plastic%20Bags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20his%20peers%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20making%20social%20media%20content%2C%20Mohammed%20Azhar%20Mohiuddin%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20delve%20into%20entrepreneurship%20and%20tackle%20pressing%20issues%20such%20as%20plastic%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20young%20age%2C%20he%20dabbled%20in%20various%20ventures%20from%20website%20development%2C%20logo%20designing%2C%20to%20running%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%20to%20selling%20burgers%20from%20home.%20His%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%20was%20fueled%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20solve%20problems%20rather%20than%20solely%20chasing%20financial%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20I%20wondered%20what%20I%20was%20really%20even%20chasing.%20Money%3F%20That%20would%20come%20even%20after%20I%20started%20focusing%20on%20solving%20real%20life%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20on%20top%20global%20environmental%20issues%2C%20Azhar%20found%20that%20there%20have%20been%20several%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20protests%20worldwide%20on%20plastic%20pollution.%20%E2%80%9CUnless%20we%20have%20an%20alternative%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20curb%20plastic%20usage.%20While%20big%20brands%20can%20afford%20jute%20and%20cloth%20bags%20but%20medium%20and%20small%20businesses%20which%20comprise%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20Indian%20market%20continue%20to%20use%20plastic%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20plastic%20bags%20are%20its%20properties.%20It%20is%20water%20resistant%2C%20thermal%2C%20durable%2C%20light-weight%2C%20and%20has%20good%20tensile%20strength.%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%20that%20could%20mirror%20the%20properties%20of%20plastic%20while%20being%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cheaper%20than%20paper%2C%20cloth%2C%20and%20jute%20alternatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%98Bio%20Reform%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20startup%20that%20manufactures%20compostable%20bags%20using%20corn%20waste%2C%20sugars%2C%20cellulose%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20components%20into%20sustainable%20biopolymers.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20it%20has%20replaced%20over%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azhar%20is%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup