47%2Ffarmers-income-aneesh-jain-gram-unnati-value-chain-rajasthan-agri-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarket%20linkage%20facilities%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20was%20allotted%20a%20sale%20booth%20at%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bachittar%20runs%20an%20automatic%20plant%20to%20process%20soybeans%20into%20milk%20and%20tofu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20prepares%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Enamkeen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emathri%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20by-products%20from%20the%20residual%20waste.%20Marketed%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Vigour%20Soy%20Health%20Milk%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20has%20developed%20a%20huge%20customer%20base%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20Sangrur%2C%20Dhuri%2C%20Barnala%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20and%20Rajpura%20districts%2C%20clocking%20an%20annual%20sales%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2048%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20being%20a%20debt-ridden%20farmer%20to%20award%20winning%20agricultural%20processor%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20becoming%20a%20pioneer%20in%20soybean%20cultivation%2C%20farming%20was%20not%20a%20bed%20of%20roses%20for%20Bachittar.%20Until%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20he%20reaped%20huge%20profits%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244135%2Fwest-bengal-potato-farming-women-farmers-empowerment-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20potatoes%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20unexpected%20glut%20in%20the%20market%20incurred%20him%20losses%20of%20Rs%203%20crores.%20His%20produce%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20cold%20storage%20for%20three%20consecutive%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetween%201998%20and%202001%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20potatoes%20at%20all%20due%20to%20a%20surplus%20and%20there%20was%20a%20very%20low%20demand.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20purchase%20a%20Rs%202%20packet%20of%20salt.%20%3Cem%3EUske%20bhi%20mer